## MockData type

Represents the data produced by an invocation of a mock, ready for assertion.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export type MockData<AllSetupInfo, T extends string> = {
    config: SetupInfoFor<AllSetupInfo, T>;
    assertableData: () => Promise<MockOutput>;
};
```
